1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:03,702
ControlX is an evidence console for authorized Web research.

2
00:00:03,652 --> 00:00:06,879
The scope gate records the target and explicit approval.

3
00:00:06,879 --> 00:00:14,947
One click runs a bounded, read-only Web audit to capture headers, routes,
cookies, CORS behavior, and reproduction commands.

4
00:00:14,947 --> 00:00:19,015
Surface Map shows the safely reached routes and candidate signals.

5
00:00:19,015 --> 00:00:26,254
When a claim needs proof, the same-state IDOR replay proves legitimate access,
then demonstrates victim-private data exposure.

6
00:00:26,254 --> 00:00:30,152
The final report packages commands, evidence, and status.

7
00:00:30,152 --> 00:00:36,788
Built in Codex with GPT-5.6 Sol, ControlX converts real signals into verifiable reports.
